{"id":221312,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/04/维权网-北京张贴公告羞辱拆迁户，只缘张悦向法/","date":"2012-04-19T07:21:50Z","modified":"2012-04-19T07:21:50Z","title":"维权网 | 北京张贴公告羞辱拆迁户，只缘张悦向法院起诉（图）","content":"<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" name=\"more\"></a>（维权网信息员张宁宁报道）<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span>日，北京市东城区西革新里危改项目拆迁协调指挥部超越职权，在拆迁地区的醒目位置张贴告示，羞辱张悦等拆迁户。该告示夸大事实，泄露多名拆迁户的隐私，造成了严重的负面影响。该拆迁指挥部张贴告示的真正原因是，张悦抢在行政裁决前向法院提起行政诉讼，导致房管局无法作出裁决，更使该拆迁指挥部恼羞成怒，故贴出长达<span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span>页的告示，羞辱其眼中的“钉子户”。对此，该指挥部还不过瘾，雇佣外来人员，开着一辆无牌车，车顶上安装二个高音喇叭，并标称为<span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span>综合执法<span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span>，不分昼夜一遍又一遍地宣读“告示”，穿街走巷。这不仅影响附近居民休息，还给未签订拆迁安置协议的拆迁户造成莫大的精神压力。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>次日上午<span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span>点许，该指挥部再返回张悦住房附近，继续宣读“告示”，有<span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span>户被点名，或称其无理要求；或称其采取了卑劣手段等。其中，评价张悦：“无理要求，并采取通过行政诉讼的卑劣手段企图逃避行政裁决，拒不办理搬迁手续。”张悦感到愤怒的是，提起行政诉讼是法律赋予公民的权利，何以成为“卑劣的手段”？<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>张悦认为，该指挥部的行为侵犯其隐私权，公告的内容极尽诽谤之能事。张悦得知“告示”广播中提到了自己的名字，便拦截了该宣传车，立即向<span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span>报警求援；向<span lang=\"EN-US\">122</span>举报无牌车辆违法扰民；向<span lang=\"EN-US\">12345</span>市长电话反映指挥部越权执法。街坊们也闻讯赶来，纷纷指责指挥部执法违法，声援张悦的维权行为。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>民警到达现场，责令该宣传车暂停播放，但未对其作出处理，并自称无权处罚，未予以调查记录，而将违法宣传车放行。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">12345</span><span>市长电话的工作人员向该宣传车司机询问缘由，司机又向指挥部汇报。该指挥部领导董某赶到现场。当<span lang=\"EN-US\">12345</span>市长电话的工作人员请董某接电话，但他若无其事地说<span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span>我没有必要接市长热线电话。<span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">122</span><span>交通队接到张悦举报后，一直没有露面。这辆无照牌的<span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span>综合执法<span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span>宣传车在众目睽睽之下，堂而皇之地开走了。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>张悦表示，她将针对该指挥部的违法行为，提起行政诉讼，维护自己的合法权益。</span></div>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-Ohc4k5NZZJU/T4qclmz9MzI/AAAAAAAAGmU/xFz2TMWFaGU/s1600/%E6%97%A0%E7%89%8C%E6%B1%BD%E8%BD%A6%E6%89%A7%E6%B3%95.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"216\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-Ohc4k5NZZJU/T4qclmz9MzI/AAAAAAAAGmU/xFz2TMWFaGU/s320/%E6%97%A0%E7%89%8C%E6%B1%BD%E8%BD%A6%E6%89%A7%E6%B3%95.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-HfaRPqo0qWM/T4qZBVhSO6I/AAAAAAAAGk8/zGnJ0ZCDOg0/s1600/1.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-HfaRPqo0qWM/T4qZBVhSO6I/AAAAAAAAGk8/zGnJ0ZCDOg0/s320/1.JPG\" width=\"208\" /></a></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-V-R2Fh-EXr4/T4qf_xU3uqI/AAAAAAAAGm0/kTdmaHXKiN0/s1600/2.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-V-R2Fh-EXr4/T4qf_xU3uqI/AAAAAAAAGm0/kTdmaHXKiN0/s320/2.JPG\" width=\"209\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-iXQKw6gQD2U/T4qgN2K4I7I/AAAAAAAAGm8/HYq_xx1xrq0/s1600/3.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-iXQKw6gQD2U/T4qgN2K4I7I/AAAAAAAAGm8/HYq_xx1xrq0/s320/3.JPG\" width=\"213\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-XCb8tTcvrr8/T4qgjf00_ZI/AAAAAAAAGnE/v-EfSKV7ZCw/s1600/4.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-XCb8tTcvrr8/T4qgjf00_ZI/AAAAAAAAGnE/v-EfSKV7ZCw/s320/4.JPG\" width=\"213\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-JMBr6SjX6pk/T4qgxTmAZsI/AAAAAAAAGnM/cZcXyUy0-zg/s1600/5.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-JMBr6SjX6pk/T4qgxTmAZsI/AAAAAAAAGnM/cZcXyUy0-zg/s320/5.JPG\" width=\"218\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-KTdbDvNLzLk/T4qhB961dfI/AAAAAAAAGnU/yNf32F01-Pk/s1600/6.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-KTdbDvNLzLk/T4qhB961dfI/AAAAAAAAGnU/yNf32F01-Pk/s320/6.JPG\" width=\"216\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-3Z4U7MAR2v4/T4qhUE8BbRI/AAAAAAAAGnc/Zie55ZBxS-Y/s1600/7.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-3Z4U7MAR2v4/T4qhUE8BbRI/AAAAAAAAGnc/Zie55ZBxS-Y/s320/7.JPG\" width=\"210\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img alt=\"\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-2260392006525070432?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" width=\"1\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n","author":1004,"categories":[1],"tags":[]}